1
00:00:04,636 --> 00:00:10,642
<i>September 21, 1945...
That was the night I died.</i>

2
00:00:41,464 --> 00:00:43,424
Damn tramps...

3
00:00:43,883 --> 00:00:46,177
Watch it!

4
00:00:46,261 --> 00:00:47,428
Disgusting!

5
00:00:47,512 --> 00:00:48,972
Is he dead?

6
00:00:49,013 --> 00:00:51,099
The Americans will be
arriving any day now...

7
00:00:51,182 --> 00:00:54,102
It's disgraceful,
having these bums here!

8
00:01:03,361 --> 00:01:05,280
Mama---!

9
00:01:06,656 --> 00:01:10,118
What day is it?

10
00:01:20,795 --> 00:01:23,131
Setsuko...

11
00:01:32,849 --> 00:01:35,143
Another one.

12
00:01:48,489 --> 00:01:50,074
What is
this stuff?

13
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:53,119
Never mind.
Just dump it!

14
00:02:05,256 --> 00:02:07,175
This one's a goner, too.

15
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:10,762
You can see
it in their eyes...

